This are the files provided by UPMC. 
Only a little modification in link and joint name was done by hand:
  * link "waist" was renamed in "root_link" (for having a clear root_link)
  * joint "neck_pitch" was renamed in "head_pitch" (for using the same joint names define in http://wiki.icub.org/wiki/ICub_joints)
  * joint "neck_roll" was renamed in "head_roll" (for using the same joint names defined in http://wiki.icub.org/wiki/ICub_joints)
  * joint "neck_yaw" was renamed in "head_yaw" (for using the same joint names defined in http://wiki.icub.org/wiki/ICub_joints)